lead_paragraph: Wales are happy to cast themselves as underdogs in their Euro 2016 quarter-final against Belgium on Friday but such modesty belies their proven ability to bite hard.

headline.print_headline: Rival Golden Generations of Wales, Belgium Bid for Glory
